
    A 33-year-old police detective Constable stationed at
Saselamani police station outside Malamulele 
has been arrested for alleged corruption.HAWKS spokesperson Matimba Maluleke said the suspect
allegedly demanded R1200 from the suspect whom he had arrested for possession
of suspected stolen property in exchange of bail.It was further alleged that the suspect went to the
